    public class PrinterSettings
extends java.lang.Object

      • PrinterSettings

        public PrinterSettings(java.lang.String printerName,
               int paperWidth,
               int printerResolution,
               PaperKind paperKind)
        Create a new PrinterSettings instance with the given values.
        Parameters:
        printerName - the name of the printer. This parameter must not be null.
        paperWidth - the width of the paper, in millimeters.
        printerResolution - the resolution of the printer in DPI.
        paperKind - the kind of paper. This parameter must not be null.
